Title: Love on fire
DateModified: '2019-02-14'
DatePublished: '2019-02-14'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/love-on-fire
SetInCountry: Greece
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Gabriela Dia
AuthorCountry: France
Text: "A shy girl from USA decides to visit a Italian island as a graduation present,\
  \ she has no idea what to do next on her life. She\u2019s lost, she needs to discover\
  \ what she really wants and that\u2019s why she picked randomly that island. She\
  \ starts falling in love with culture, the music, the people, but then she meets\
  \ someone completely different to who she is use to know, he teach her to be more\
  \ open to life and try new experiences. He helps her to get to know her own self,\
  \ however this guy is in troubles, he used to be part of the Italian mafia and they\
  \ are looking for him after betraying the leader (which is his step father)."
